---
title: Alpine Turkey Burgers with Mushrooms, Swiss Cheese, Dijonnaise & Broccoli
description: Looking to up your turkey burger game? This version will blow your mind. The spiced patties are seared until browned, topped with buttery sautéed mushrooms and melty Swiss cheese, and stuffed into toasted potato buns. Of course, no burger would be complete without a special sauce—this one combines mayo, sour cream, and Dijon to create the perfect rich, tangy topper. Pro tip: That Dijonnaise also goes great with the garlicky potato wedges on the side.
